584
00:46:10,060 --> 00:46:12,580
Dongjun, you should head back for now.

585
00:46:12,580 --> 00:46:18,020
When we meet again, I shall impart the true Xichu's Sword Song to you.

586
00:46:18,020 --> 00:46:23,000
But Master, I'm afraid you'll be in danger if you remain here.

587
00:46:23,920 --> 00:46:25,660
Don't worry.

